### 🔊 Audio — Google SpeechCommands · CNN + Bidirectional GRU · 15 epochs · 35 classes

| Epoch | Adam | AdamW | SGD | **ΨLogic** |
|-------|------|-------|-----|-----------|
| 1  | 80.79% | 82.87% | 41.49% | 81.27% |
