| 12 | 94.98% | 95.10% | 89.83% | **95.11%** ← leads |
| 15 | **95.50%★** | 95.35% | 90.81% | 95.26% |

> ΨLogic beats AdamW at epochs 10 and 12. Final gap to Adam: **0.24%**.

